casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Brown, Appellant, v. Duramed Pharmaceuticals, Inc. et al., Appellees.

[Cite as State ex rel. Brown v. Duramed Pharmaceuticals, Inc., 107 Ohio St.3d 295, 2005-Ohio-6512.]

*296(No. 2005-0562 Submitted October 25, 2005 Decided December 28, 2005.) Butkovich, Crosthwaite & Gast Co., L.P.A., and Daryl A.W. Crosthwaite, for appellant. Jim Petro, Attorney General, and Shawn M. Wollam, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee Industrial Commission of Ohio.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed consistent with the opinion of the court of appeals.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
